Build SupremeBeats as a premium AI music creator platform and social network.
Use simple, clean React components.
Do not delete working files unless asked.
Keep the design cinematic, dark, premium, and modern.
Prefer editing existing files over creating duplicate versions.
Explain major changes before applying them.

**Site URL:** When constructing any full URL that points to this app (auth callbacks, email links, share links, canonical URLs, etc.), use `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` as the base (e.g. `${process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL}/auth/confirm`). Do not hardcode `https://supremebeatsstudio.com` or any `.vercel.app` URL so one env value controls the domain everywhere.
